  <brief_title>Sorafenib Gastric Cancer Asian Phase I Study</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase I Study to Investigate Safety, Pharmacokinetics and Preliminary Efficacy Profile of Sorafenib (BAY 43-9006) in Combination With S-1 Plus CDDP in Asian Patients With Unresectable / Recurrent Gastric Cancer</official_title>
