  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is to investigate safety, pharmacokinetics and preliminary efficacy profile of
      sorafenib in combination with S-1 plus cisplatin in Asian patients with unresectable /
      recurrent gastric cancer.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
